snippet.title: Learn To Code RPG - Game Promo
snippet.description:
In this brand new game from freeCodeCamp, you will attempt to learn to code so you can get a developer job. 

Get the game on Itch: https://freecodecamp.itch.io/learn-to-code-rpg
Get the game on GitHub: https://github.com/freeCodeCamp/LearnToCodeRPG 

❤️ Support for this channel comes from our friends at Scrimba – the coding platform that's reinvented interactive learning: https://scrimba.com/freecodecamp
